  "title": "Staff Nurse ( ICU Trained ), Up 7.5 K, Shifts Required #HVY",
  "description": "<p></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p></p><ul><li>To Care for patient needs throughout their recovery in the ICU unit</li><li>To Complete all necessary paperwork before transferring a patient</li><li>To Maintain patient records</li><li>To Create and implement effective care plans</li><li>Any other ad hoc duties assigned</li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Registered with Singapore Nursing Board.</li><li>Minimum Diploma in Nursing or equivalent.</li><li>Candidates with Advanced Nursing Diploma in Critical Care Nursing or equivalent will have an advantage</li><li>At least 3 years of experience in Intensive Care Unit.</li><li>Able to work on 12 hours shifts (including night shift)</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p></p><p><u><strong>valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></u></p><p></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
